title: Miles Davis Kind Of Blue [FLAC+MP3](Big Papi) 1997 Remaster Jazz
description:
Source: 1997 Columbia CK 64935 CD



Listen up. Two tracks (5 & 6) kept ripping with error codes but the source disc is like new and the hash codes were consistent making Big Papi think the codes in the online database may not be correct. All tracks were tested and no error artifacts could be detected during play. Make your download decision based on this please.

Big Papi scanned the back cover so check it out for information on how this remastered CD is different from previous CD releases. It claims previous masters were playing at wrong speeds. It also states "old school" sound engineering equipment was used in order to get the original warmth. Big Papi is playing the MP3 files right now trough some NHT loudspeakers and the sound is crisp just like Miles is here is the room with that trumpet.

- Big Papi
